    "description": "<br><br>1910年法国哥特式推理惊悚小说<br>用现代人的视角重新诠释“歌剧魅影”的冒险游戏。<br>“MazM：歌剧魅影”即将登陆任天堂Switch！<br><br>引起歌剧院骚乱的“歌剧魅影”事件数十年以后，<br>有“侦探”突然来访巴黎歌剧院，<br>此行的目的是调查几十年前那起“歌剧魅影”事件的真相……<br><br>收集人物信息和百科全书，去解开隐藏在歌剧院内的真相！<br>“他”藏在暗处，洞悉一切，时刻关注着事态的发展……<br>一个激情燃烧的爱情故事，一个充满仇恨的爱情故事，打破了歌剧院的平静。<br><br>充满19世纪末法国美好时代独特氛围的画面，突显登场人物个性的角色，加上增强代入感的经典音频！超越原著小说、创新剧情的冒险游戏“MazM：歌剧魅影”。<br>去破解歌剧院里发生的神秘事件，感受让人心惊肉跳的凄美爱情故事！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483300/extras/3bbdce7e025036fcca63fb00eca0712b.poster.avif?t=1616655841\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483300/extras/3bbdce7e025036fcca63fb00eca0712b.webm?t=1616655841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483300/extras/3bbdce7e025036fcca63fb00eca0712b.mp4?t=1616655841\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483300/extras/9e0fc232dbf661a5f480dd2ebb51850a.poster.avif?t=1616655841\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483300/extras/9e0fc232dbf661a5f480dd2ebb51850a.webm?t=1616655841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483300/extras/9e0fc232dbf661a5f480dd2ebb51850a.mp4?t=1616655841\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483300/extras/cfcc6f582a4808d9b6d4d39495b2830d.poster.avif?t=1616655841\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/148